kw.name: Run Jmeter
kw.doc: Runs JMeter. Returns None. Parameters: - jmeterPath - path to JMeter executable file - testPlanPath - path to jmx file - logFilePath - path to a log file - otherParams (optional) - other parameters to be called Examples: | run jmeter | D:/apache-jmeter-2.12/bin/jmeter.bat | D:/Tests/Test1Thread1Loop.jmx | D:/Tests/output1.jtl | | run jmeter | D:/apache-jmeter-2.12/bin/jmeter.bat | D:/Tests/Test1Thread1Loop.jmx | D:/Tests/output1.jtl | -H my.proxy.server -P 8000 |
kw.msg: Starting JMeter with following parameters: - JMeter path: C:/JMeter/apache-jmeter-5.6.2/bin/jmeter.bat - Test plan path: C:/Jmeter report/Robot_JMeter.jmx - Log file path: C:/Jmeter_JTL/re.jtl - Other parameters: . subprocess.call input list: ['C:/JMeter/apache-jmeter-5.6.2/bin/jmeter.bat', '-n', '-t', 'C:/Jmeter report/Robot_JMeter.jmx', '-l', 'C:/Jmeter_JTL/re.jtl'] Value returned by JMeter: 0
